title: H2 Solutions
author: Zizon Technology
description: H2 Solutions Pte Ltd is a young and dynamic organisation mainly providing sales and rental of Multifunction Photocopiers and Printers in terms of hardware. Aiming to become a “One-Stop IT Solutions” company to our customers, we also specialise in Computers and Computer Peripherals, as well as other Office and Business Solutions. Founded in 2014, H2 solutions is managed by a team of very experienced staff in the IT Solutions Industry.
